<title>API Reference &mdash; Veld</title>
<style>
/* ── Reset ── */
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

/* ── Design tokens ── */
:root {
  --bg:         #f8fafc;
  --fg:         #0f172a;
